    "description": [
      "Seawater swirls slowly on the ground, carrying bits of muck toward a deep sucking sinkhole near the water's edge.  Up above, on a bluff with steeply cragged sides, rest signs of civilization in the rooftops and palisade walls of a small village.  Despite the buildings' presence, the breeze carries only the cries of gulls and the roar of the crashing waves."
